            <h2>July 25, 2010 - January 2013</h2>
            <p>The church organization which is mainly composed of volunteer/ non-paid faithful workers was re-established on July 25, 2010 with its senior pastor Alberto “AL” Dones. Since then, general meeting has been a regular monthly activity. God continued to provide workers for the church; non-paid yet are committed to do the great commission. The church is now a full gospel Christian organization of strong leadership with 200+ members as of January 2013.</p>
